; Issue: https://github.com/rustledger/rustledger/issues/251
; Description: Tolerance handling should match beancount's more lenient behavior
; Expected: No errors - beancount tolerates larger discrepancies in some cases

option "operating_currency" "USD"

2000-01-01 open Assets:Abc ABC
2000-01-01 open Expenses:Abc USD

2026-01-01 * "Transaction with cost basis rounding"
  Assets:Abc    70.538 ABC {100 USD}
  Expenses:Abc
